501
00:31:56,081 --> 00:31:59,882
<i>Tha thứ cho con.</i>
<i>Con xin lỗi.</i>

502
00:31:59,918 --> 00:32:06,589
Con xin--Con thực sự xin lỗi.
Con--

503
00:32:09,661 --> 00:32:12,228
Jesus.

